1
00:00:59,640 --> 00:01:01,759
Shengxiutang.

2
00:01:02,399 --> 00:01:03,359
What does it mean?

3
00:01:04,239 --> 00:01:05,480
Why is the clinic named like this?

4
00:01:05,799 --> 00:01:07,159
Be benevolent and virtuous.

5
00:01:07,799 --> 00:01:08,920
Improve yourself and help others.

6
00:01:09,480 --> 00:01:11,079
It also requires us doctors

7
00:01:12,280 --> 00:01:13,719
to be compassionate

8
00:01:13,920 --> 00:01:16,519
and improve our moral cultivation.

9
00:01:17,079 --> 00:01:19,239
This is the name given by my great-grandfather.

10
00:01:20,239 --> 00:01:21,200
Great-grandfather?

11
00:01:21,519 --> 00:01:22,840
That must be many years ago.

12
00:01:23,319 --> 00:01:23,840
Yes.

13
00:01:25,079 --> 00:01:26,319
My writing isn't good.

14
00:01:26,400 --> 00:01:27,000
Jin,

15
00:01:27,200 --> 00:01:28,359
if you don't mind,

16
00:01:28,879 --> 00:01:29,640
I'll give it to you.

17
00:01:30,000 --> 00:01:31,120
I don't mind at all, uncle.

18
00:01:31,439 --> 00:01:32,120
Thank you, uncle.

19
00:01:32,319 --> 00:01:34,439
I should be thanking you for your help.

20
00:01:34,719 --> 00:01:35,680
It's nothing,

21
00:01:36,040 --> 00:01:36,760
just a small thing, Lin Hao.

22
00:01:37,680 --> 00:01:39,519
How about we add some acupuncture cases

23
00:01:39,640 --> 00:01:42,159
to this storyboard?

24
00:01:42,319 --> 00:01:42,799
What do you think?

25
00:01:43,879 --> 00:01:44,439
Sounds good.

26
00:01:44,760 --> 00:01:46,439
Many people are interested in acupoints,

27
00:01:46,840 --> 00:01:47,760
but it's too obscure.

28
00:01:48,159 --> 00:01:49,640
Animation can make it more accessible.

29
00:01:49,959 --> 00:01:50,680
Sure.

30
00:01:51,239 --> 00:01:51,959
Here, take this.

31
00:01:58,159 --> 00:01:59,439
I made chicken soup for everyone.

32
00:01:59,640 --> 00:02:00,280
To boost your health.

33
00:02:02,280 --> 00:02:03,239
Thank you, Auntie Du.

34
00:02:04,640 --> 00:02:05,400
Did you burn your hand?

35
00:02:15,120 --> 00:02:15,840
Fei,

36
00:02:16,280 --> 00:02:17,120
thank you for coming.

37
00:02:17,639 --> 00:02:18,800
You finally got a break,

38
00:02:18,879 --> 00:02:20,000
and you've been busy all day.

39
00:02:20,280 --> 00:02:21,240
When are you going back?

40
00:02:21,879 --> 00:02:23,719
When I become a part of this family,

41
00:02:24,080 --> 00:02:24,759
I'll go back.

42
00:02:29,360 --> 00:02:30,000
It won't be long.

43
00:02:30,520 --> 00:02:31,879
The wedding date is set.

44
00:02:32,199 --> 00:02:34,479
We'll be a family soon.

45
00:02:44,800 --> 00:02:45,280
Lin,

46
00:02:45,800 --> 00:02:46,479
what's wrong with you?

47
00:02:48,120 --> 00:02:48,840
I'm fine, uncle.

48
00:02:49,360 --> 00:02:50,360
I just stayed up late these days

49
00:02:50,520 --> 00:02:51,240
and caught a bit of a cold.

50
00:02:51,599 --> 00:02:52,240
You've been working hard.

51
00:02:52,479 --> 00:02:54,680
Must be from working on the promotional video.

52
00:02:56,919 --> 00:02:57,560
Xiaochuan,

53
00:02:57,919 --> 00:02:59,400
get some ginseng for Lin.

54
00:03:00,560 --> 00:03:01,639
Here, have this.

55
00:03:02,080 --> 00:03:02,520
Here you go.

56
00:03:04,080 --> 00:03:04,840
Thank you, Xiaochuan.

57
00:03:05,560 --> 00:03:06,120
No problem.

58
00:03:23,840 --> 00:03:24,400
Jin,

59
00:03:25,000 --> 00:03:25,800
what's wrong with you?

60
00:03:26,360 --> 00:03:27,159
I'm fine, uncle.

61
00:03:27,520 --> 00:03:29,240
I'm having a bit of a headache.

62
00:03:29,400 --> 00:03:30,319
Must be the water and food.

63
00:03:32,319 --> 00:03:33,240
Let me check on you.

64
00:03:33,840 --> 00:03:34,759
Could you grab a bowl for me?

65
00:03:35,039 --> 00:03:35,520
Lin Hao,

66
00:03:36,159 --> 00:03:37,319
could you look after Caien?

67
00:03:44,120 --> 00:03:44,520
Right,

68
00:03:45,039 --> 00:03:45,520
just here.

69
00:03:46,319 --> 00:03:46,879
That's the spot.

70
00:03:47,400 --> 00:03:48,120
Feels great.

71
00:03:48,719 --> 00:03:49,400
That's the spot.

72
00:03:52,520 --> 00:03:53,120
Right here.

73
00:03:54,800 --> 00:03:55,800
So good.

74
00:03:56,439 --> 00:03:57,240
So good.

75
00:03:57,960 --> 00:03:58,439
Xiao Chuan,

76
00:04:01,120 --> 00:04:02,240
see, Xiao Fei

77
00:04:02,560 --> 00:04:03,919
is a real gentleman.

78
00:04:06,159 --> 00:04:07,000
Come on, another sip.

79
00:04:07,039 --> 00:04:07,639
Brother,

80
00:04:08,199 --> 00:04:09,120
I'll do it myself.

81
00:04:09,439 --> 00:04:10,080
It's okay.

82
00:04:11,639 --> 00:04:12,879
So good.

83
00:04:13,319 --> 00:04:14,159
Brother,

84
00:04:32,720 --> 00:04:34,480
wipe your mouth, it's all over your lips.

85
00:04:36,160 --> 00:04:36,879
What are you doing?

86
00:04:40,439 --> 00:04:40,920
Brother,

87
00:04:41,720 --> 00:04:42,560
come here.

88
00:04:42,720 --> 00:04:44,000
I have something to tell you.

89
00:04:45,639 --> 00:04:46,040
Dad,

90
00:04:46,560 --> 00:04:47,800
I'll talk to my brother for a moment.

91
00:04:48,360 --> 00:04:48,759
Okay.

92
00:05:03,920 --> 00:05:04,879
What exactly do you want to do?

93
00:05:05,800 --> 00:05:06,600
What did I do?

94
00:05:08,279 --> 00:05:09,279
My dad is here.

95
00:05:09,279 --> 00:05:11,120
You're touching me.

96
00:05:11,879 --> 00:05:12,839
Taking care of my sister

97
00:05:13,560 --> 00:05:15,360
How can it be inappropriate?

98
00:05:15,639 --> 00:05:16,560
Who is your sister?

99
00:05:20,759 --> 00:05:21,600
Then what are you to me?

100
00:05:22,680 --> 00:05:24,160
I'm warning you for the last time.

101
00:05:24,519 --> 00:05:25,279
The last time.

102
00:05:27,279 --> 00:05:28,560
If you do this again, I'll beat you up.

103
00:05:29,839 --> 00:05:31,639
Your bangs are showing.

104
00:05:51,000 --> 00:05:52,040
You're over the line.

105
00:05:53,600 --> 00:05:54,680
I think it's just right.

106
00:05:57,399 --> 00:05:58,920
You don't let go after breaking up.

107
00:06:00,240 --> 00:06:01,319
It's not a gentleman's behavior.

108
00:06:03,439 --> 00:06:04,800
Yunfei

109
00:06:05,319 --> 00:06:06,399
Lin Hao said

110
00:06:06,720 --> 00:06:08,560
you were still bothering her after breaking up.

111
00:06:09,040 --> 00:06:10,040
You are a

112
00:06:10,399 --> 00:06:11,600
bad guy.

113
00:06:15,639 --> 00:06:17,399
He just misses her.

114
00:06:23,120 --> 00:06:24,639
I think he is a good guy.

115
00:06:24,839 --> 00:06:25,800
There's nothing wrong.

116
00:06:32,839 --> 00:06:33,680
See?

117
00:06:34,040 --> 00:06:35,439
They are a team.

118
00:06:36,040 --> 00:06:37,199
Don't be self-righteous.

119
00:07:28,000 --> 00:07:28,879
What are you doing here?

120
00:07:33,639 --> 00:07:34,480
You drank?

121
00:07:37,319 --> 00:07:38,319
I missed you.

122
00:07:44,519 --> 00:07:45,199
Where are you going?

123
00:07:45,360 --> 00:07:46,560
To bed.

124
00:08:07,279 --> 00:08:07,800
Fine.

125
00:08:09,279 --> 00:08:10,319
Do whatever you want.

126
00:08:10,680 --> 00:08:11,720
But let's get this straight,

127
00:08:12,079 --> 00:08:13,600
I didn't touch you at all.

128
00:08:49,759 --> 00:08:50,360
Is there a problem?

129
00:08:51,759 --> 00:08:52,720
My hand...

130
00:09:16,840 --> 00:09:18,840
I... I need to tell you something.

131
00:09:23,639 --> 00:09:24,320
I...

132
00:09:27,120 --> 00:09:28,639
still like you.

133
00:10:23,759 --> 00:10:24,440
What are you doing?

134
00:11:04,279 --> 00:11:05,279
Don't get drunk and make a mess.

135
00:11:07,960 --> 00:11:08,480
Lin Hao,

136
00:11:10,679 --> 00:11:11,519
did you break up with me

137
00:11:12,720 --> 00:11:13,960
because of Lan Xiaochuan?
